Author: ItsLilly22
Text: Haha omg I had forgotten that being underweight can make you lose your period. I didn’t menstruate for 9 months back when I was heavy restricting some years ago, man I miss that. I hate the bleeding and the cramps sm. Now I have even more motivation to never eat again.

Author: stegasaurus-
Text: yeah I feel this. whenever I get my period i’m like ‘ugh i must be such a fat piece of shit’ because my body is working like a human body should??? logic
